E = hc/λ - φ = 6.626x10^-34 J s x 2.998x10^8 m/s / 300x10^-9 m - 2.40 eV x 1.602x10^-19 J/eV = 2.77x10^-19 J v = sqrt(2E/m_e) = sqrt(2 x 2.77x10^-19 J / 9.109x10^-31 kg) = 7.80x10^5 m/s n = E_total/E_photon = 3.25x10^-3 J / (6.626x10^-34 J s x 2.998x10^8 m/s / 300x10^-9 m) = 4.91x10^15 electrons.
